<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1996—Subsec. (a)(2). <ref href="/us/pl/104/324">Pub. L. 104–324</ref> inserted “as measured under <ref href="/us/usc/t46/s14502">section 14502 of this title</ref>, or an alternate tonnage measured under <ref href="/us/usc/t46/s14302">section 14302 of this title</ref> as prescribed by the Secretary under <ref href="/us/usc/t46/s14104">section 14104 of this title</ref>” after “75 gross tons”.</p>
